window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>FBI Agents Otto and Gaspar pick up where Lee Child's <i>The Enemy</i> leaves off in the Hunt for Jack Reacher. </p> <p>When FBI Special Agents Kim Otto and Carlos Gaspar are sent to Fort Bird, North Carolina, to find Jack Reacher, powerful enemies with their backs against the wall will stop at nothing to keep the secrets Reacher left behind. The Hunt for Jack Reacher series enthralls fans of John Grisham, Lee Child, and more. </p>"; 
